---
title: Mild Ginger & Coconut Beef with Greens & Garlic Rice
description: Asian-inspired cuisine comes together in a flash tonight. The secret? We’ve doubled up on superstar ingredients, with an aromatic ginger-lemongrass coconut sauce and garlic rice so it smells and tastes like a tropical holiday.
